Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.79,0:01:05.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,醒醒  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:05.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.96,0:01:07.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在要来看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:07.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.00,0:01:09.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村新闻  主持人是帕奇帕金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:09.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom News with Perch Perkins
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:10.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,248)}海胆哥与败蜗子秀
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.30,0:01:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有道理  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thinking, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.01,0:01:16.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新闻可能会颠三倒四
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:16.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The news can be pretty topsy-turvy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:19.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(418,512)}裤头村\N新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.34,0:01:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下面是今晚要闻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In tonight's top story
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.14,0:01:24.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本地一只松鼠受困井中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:24.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a local squirrel got stuck in a well
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.77,0:01:25.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:25.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.94,0:01:28.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救我出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:28.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get me outta here, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.10,0:01:30.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管那位是谁都一定很尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:30.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be embarrassing for whoever that is
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.57,0:01:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但今天起先  机械智能发生了巨变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:33.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But first, radical changes in machine intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,were made today
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.65,0:01:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正好这时候有只本地松鼠困在了井里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when a local squirrel got stuck in a well
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.00,0:01:48.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来再也用不着这些懒鬼消防员了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like we won't be needing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:48.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,those lazy firemen anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1278,170)}最新消息
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.21,0:01:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This just in
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本地电视台新闻记者帕奇帕金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Local TV news reporter Perch Perkins
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.88,0:01:56.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已被开除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:56.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has been fired
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.09,0:01:59.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:01:59.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fired?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fired?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.31,0:02:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长期从事本地新闻工作的资深人士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The long-time local news veteran
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.43,0:02:07.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即将被最新的新闻报道科技
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is being replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:07.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by the latest in reporting technology
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.81,0:02:10.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新闻机2000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:10.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Newsbot 2000
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,立刻替代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,effective immediately
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.73,0:02:13.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:13.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.61,0:02:14.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:14.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Perch
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能这么对我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't do this to me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.53,0:02:18.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在裤头村新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:18.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We here at Bikini Bottom News
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,致敬你长年以来为大众的服务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,salute you for your years of service
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让你带走任何公司财物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't let you leave with any company property
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能最起码留着盒子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't I at least keep the box?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.30,0:02:35.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以留的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:35.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.59,0:02:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是头发归演播室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the hair belongs to the studio
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是假发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a toupee
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个机器不可能替代帕奇这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A robot could never replace someone like Perch
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.82,0:02:57.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我们心中的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:57.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in our hearts
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.90,0:03:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不能坐视不管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't stand for this
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去给那家新闻演播室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna give that news studio
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.37,0:03:03.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点颜色瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:03.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a piece of my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:03.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(960,920)}头 脑
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We want Perch
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We want Perch
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让帕奇回归
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring back Perch
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可否跟各位观众详细介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you care to tell the folks back home more
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的抗议内容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about your protest?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.30,0:03:22.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕奇帕金斯可是我全海洋最爱的记者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, Perch Perkins is my favorite newsman
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the whole ocean
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.43,0:03:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perch?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.76,0:03:28.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,禁止逗留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:28.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No loitering
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你身为帕奇帕金斯的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As a fan of Perch Perkins
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如何评价机器人接替他职位一事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what do you think about a robot taking his job?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器绝对不能拿来替代人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't just replace someone with a machine
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.23,0:03:40.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大机  代我抗议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:40.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat-tron, take over this protest for me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.86,0:03:41.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:41.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perch
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.65,0:03:42.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:42.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.70,0:03:50.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:50.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老记者巷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old Reporters Row
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.50,0:03:57.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电视台的记者全在这度过停播时光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:57.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where TV reporters finish out their off-air years
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最低温度55度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Low of 55
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.76,0:04:02.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最高温度72度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,High of 72
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本次要闻有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our top stories--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交还给你  鲍勃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to you, Bob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perch
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不属于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't belong here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还信任你的早餐麦片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you trust your breakfast cereal?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王的皇冠是否太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is King Neptune's crown too small?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,究竟是支持还是反对生育
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Babies: for or against?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下面是急报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's a burning story
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1024,920)}烧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.24,0:04:28.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该记者的旧报纸库存即将耗尽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:28.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This reporter's stash of old magazines is running low
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.29,0:04:30.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:30.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perch?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得帮你脱离这里才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to get you outta here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,何苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why bother?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只会握着话筒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only thing I know how to do is hold a microphone
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,何况新闻机全代我办好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Newsbot has that all sewn up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1554,352)}杂志
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有谁能雇用我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who else would hire me?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.59,0:04:45.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有很多地方都能让你发挥自己的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's lots of places
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that can use a fish of your talents
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.89,0:04:46.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:46.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我带你去看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show ya
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:51.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1088,394)}便宜货超市
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,便宜货超市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barg'n-Mart?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱这应该是很需要找个员工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose we could use someone
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,广播店内公告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make in-store announcements
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome aboard
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请注意  便宜货超市的顾客们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, Barg'n-Mart shoppers
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.91,0:05:09.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乳制品区的奶酪正在特价
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:09.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheese is on sale in the dairy aisle
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.33,0:05:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,花卉区的鲜花有超值优惠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And fresh flowers are marked down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the floral department
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:21.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1296,200)}花卉
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕奇帕金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perch Perkins
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七号通道新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aisle Seven News
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可否说说看这里发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us what happened here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Perch
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来在买腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was procuring my pickles
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.77,0:05:37.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,突然我的掌心就湿了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:37.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I noticed my palms had grown quite dewy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我发现  却已经来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alas, my realization came too late
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的双手过度劳累  变得滑腻不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My hands, slickened from exertion
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.82,0:05:48.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就扶不住美味的腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:48.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,could not hold on to their briny bounty
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这则故事分外揪心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A heart-wrenching tale
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perkins
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该通知保洁过来清理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to call for a clean up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是采访捣乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not interview the mess maker
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这些客人伤成什么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all these injured customers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:04.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(808,428)}便宜货超市
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿被腌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pickled leg
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.60,0:06:14.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:14.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perch
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还给你安排了一样工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lined up another job for ya
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(346,394)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好我在这边有熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Luckily, I know a guy here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perch
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.40,0:06:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能有过气明星加入团队还挺不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always good to have a former celebrity on the team
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝说你很会用话筒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob said you're good on the microphone
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.33,0:06:40.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我要让你负责管得来速
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:40.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, I'm putting you on drive-through duty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好些年没用过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Haven't used it in a couple of years
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始给我赚钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Start making me some money
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里我想要点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry wants to order
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要配薯条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like fries with that?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.73,0:06:58.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:58.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要升级到蟹黄堡套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like to upgrade to a Krabby Combo
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且再来一份小份汽水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and get a small soda?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是否愿意说明为什么你的健身房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like to explain why your gym
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.95,0:07:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本月已连续违反15次健康法规
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has been hit with 15 health code violations this month?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里我很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry's a busy lobster, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,直言不讳的几小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.75,0:07:22.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里我只是想要健身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:22.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry just wanted to work out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.42,0:07:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本无意要害那些想健身的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He didn't mean for all those people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get athlete's shell
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perkins
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me guess
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要开除我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're firing me?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下面是抢先报道  对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the scoop: Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕金斯  你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perch, where are you going?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.61,0:07:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回到老记者巷  我只属于那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to Old Reporter Row where I belong
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.90,0:07:48.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:48.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not giving up yet
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你别的东西全都不擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you're no good at anything else
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就只能再次报道新闻才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then you'll just have to report the news again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.66,0:07:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a plan
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托让帕金斯回归吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please take Perch back
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非带不可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have to
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是这家新闻频道的经理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As the manager of this news network
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我解释一下为什么得带他回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,give me one good reason why I should
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.76,0:08:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为帕奇帕金斯的报道的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because Perch Perkins can out-report
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能做到比你家破烂新闻机多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your dumb old Newsbot
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随时随地都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,anytime, anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想看他试试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see him try
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.98,0:08:24.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:24.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you will
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我的报道没法比他多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I can't out-report him
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他做事可机械了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The guy's a machine
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是个机器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Literally
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我相信你  帕奇帕金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I believe in you, Perch Perkins
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比就比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is on
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新闻赛开打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a news-off
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:46.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,264)}新闻赛
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们知道规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know the rules
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁能限时报道最多新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoever reports the most news in the time allowed
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁就赢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wins
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On your mark
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get set
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,News
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.01,0:09:00.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巨型海牛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:00.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The huge manatee
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今日一简单的新闻赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A simple news-off
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竟变得一发不可收拾  当时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,turned ugly today when--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,突发新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breaking news
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一场连环船祸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pile-up has left
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,令多艘船受损至无法辨识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,multiple boats mangled beyond recognition
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This just in
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.78,0:09:14.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村市中心一高层建筑严重起火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:14.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A towering inferno in downtown Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新闻快报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,News flash
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一场海啸直冲城市而来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A tidal wave is headed straight for the city
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本记者正在独家专访
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this reporter has an exclusive interview
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海啸先生  你为什么要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Wave, why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:28.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1122,166)}商务工业
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.13,0:09:37.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该让新闻更上一层楼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:37.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to turn the news up a notch
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村街道出现大量凹坑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom streets pocked with potholes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抢先
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scoop
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.97,0:09:46.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,究竟是谁一直在把老太太们打倒在地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:46.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who keeps tipping over our old ladies?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,News flash
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,通向贝壳城的大桥倒塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The bridge to Shell City has collapsed
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.69,0:09:56.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,独家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:56.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exclusive
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.45,0:10:02.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就不可能有谁能报道那么多新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:02.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no way anyone could report that much news
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unless
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神秘皮疹席卷海滩游客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mysterious rash covers beach goers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1042,336)}第一航海银行
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村银行遭劫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom bank robbed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:16.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(474,340)}蟹暴亡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:16.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1174,392)}蟹老板垃圾
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本地快餐店遭到毁坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vandals strike local fast food restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们中断这一大堆的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We interrupt this onslaught of news
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,插播一则特别报道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to bring you a special report
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,802)}特别报道
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.59,0:10:23.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本地新闻机器人  新闻机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:23.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Local news robot, Newsbot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所报道的新闻均为他所致
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has been causing the very stories he reports on
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.73,0:10:28.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他炸毁了大桥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:28.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He destroys the bridges
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抢劫了银行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He robs the banks
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.49,0:10:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还把老太太打倒在地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He tips over the old ladies
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.08,0:10:48.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而现在  他正在毁坏这辆公交的刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:48.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And right now, he is cutting the brakes on this bus
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.04,0:10:51.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而车上载满了可爱的小蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:51.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,full of adorable baby snails
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问  新闻机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Newsbot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.96,0:10:55.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如何评价你犯下的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:55.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Care to comment on your crimes?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事情不是你看来的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't what it looks like
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你已经没新闻了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like you ran out of news
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你就自己闹事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you made your own
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.51,0:11:04.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:04.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,究竟谁先谁后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, which came first?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先有新闻报道  还是先有记者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The news story or the reporter?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新  新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,N-news
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记  记者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,R-reporter
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.44,0:11:12.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老太太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:12.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old ladies
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.86,0:11:13.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船只爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:13.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exploding boats--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My face
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.15,0:11:18.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更多情况  我们采访一下路人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:18.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For more, let's go to our man on the street
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新闻机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Newsbot
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,报道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Report
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.66,0:11:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Explode
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  帕奇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Perch
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.42,0:11:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你又被雇用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you are un-fired
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新闻头发还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your news hair back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This just in
