Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
