Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
