Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Gere-bear?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.13,0:12:19.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:19.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么跑到上面去了  你这傻蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you get up there, you silly snail?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.38,0:12:23.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:23.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jump
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳啊跳跳跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jumpity-jump-jump-jump
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:32.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1462,806)}按下求救
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.72,0:12:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如遇宠物困在树上  就拉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"In case of pet in tree, pull down"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.93,0:12:31.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:31.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.61,0:12:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁呼叫消防员的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did someone call the fire department?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让一让  民众
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step aside, citizen
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.12,0:12:48.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,梯子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:48.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladder
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.74,0:12:49.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,急救箱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:49.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First aid
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.83,0:12:50.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毯子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:50.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blanket
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.62,0:12:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's hustle, people
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hustle
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I come
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.05,0:13:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在安全了  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're safe now, sonny
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.06,0:13:18.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你救了我的小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:18.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for rescuing my little Gare bear
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想当消防员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to be a firefighter
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以吗  拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I be one, please?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I please?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,职位目前没有空缺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are no openings at this time
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.83,0:13:37.62,标准-Chi,,0,900,0,,我的头骨好像碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:37.62,标准-Eng,,0,900,0,,I think I shattered my skeleton
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.38,标准-Chi,,0,600,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.38,标准-Eng,,0,600,0,,Again
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我可能会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may regret this
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.76,0:13:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是看来职位确实有了空缺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it looks like we do have an opening
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消防站再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you at the firehouse, I guess
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,608)}消防局
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没事吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You okay there, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.48,0:14:03.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前来报到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:03.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reporting for duty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把我家斑点蜗带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought my own snail-mation
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.99,0:14:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到裤头村志愿消防站
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:15.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, welcome to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Bikini Bottom Volunteer Fire Department
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,火在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the fire?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,火在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the fire?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.13,0:14:21.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要灭火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:21.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fight it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.92,0:14:23.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要灭火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:23.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fight it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.05,0:14:24.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:24.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.30,0:14:24.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:24.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.71,0:14:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我后悔了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm regretting it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里存放的是灭火用的消防水管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we keep the hoses that extinguish the fires
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水管确实灭了我的渴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, they sure extinguished my thirst
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上楼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Upstairs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是寝室  消防间隙就在这休息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the bunk room where we rest up between fires
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以挑床位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Should I pick a bunk?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  太软
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, too soft
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.99,0:14:48.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太硬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:48.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too hard
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太芭蕾舞裙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tutu?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太不平了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too lumpy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要烈火了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna start fires
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是灭火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put out fires
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱要灭火才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We put out fires
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说了算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you say so
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,菜鸟  认识一下你的志愿同事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rookie, meet your fellow volunteer
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Charmed, I'm sure
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,荣幸之至
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pleasure
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有点眼熟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look familiar
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.85,0:15:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一场火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The First Fire?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.68,0:15:21.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是史上第一场火灾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:21.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this the first fire in the history of forever?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.31,0:15:25.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我们第一次接到的消防火灾任务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:25.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the first fire we ever got called to
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们留着它做纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We keep it as a memento
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消防滑杆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire poles
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可以滑滑杆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we slide down the poles?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.32,0:15:35.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先慢着  菜鸟们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:35.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on there, greenhorns
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们得先学习要用哪一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to learn which one to use
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这根杆通往消防船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the pole to the fire boat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这根杆通往厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one's to the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好滑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's slippery
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面涂了黄油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's buttered
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这根杆通往卫生间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This pole goes to the bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就滑这根了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my ride
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这根杆通向哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where does this pole go?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那根是神秘滑杆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That one's the mystery pole
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.81,0:15:59.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每次通向的地方都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:59.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It never goes to the same place twice
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love a mystery
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.10,0:16:02.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:02.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.69,0:16:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种疯玩意要怎么停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you stop this crazy thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踩刹车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit the brakes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.29,0:16:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.06,0:16:39.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还爱神秘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:39.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you still love a mystery?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最近几天不怎么爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so much these days
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,列队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Line up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也来做志愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You volunteered too?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.69,0:16:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,法院强制他来志愿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was court-mandated for this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.45,0:16:56.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他却派我来冒名顶替
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:56.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but sent me in his stead
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是代理的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a proxy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  代理的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, proxy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是盒子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm boxy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是媚气的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm foxy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就是逃避的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, then I'm an escapee
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.38,0:17:07.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:07.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.83,0:17:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都听好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen up
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.75,0:17:10.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是训练区
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:10.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the training area
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们三个之所以来志愿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The reason why there are three of you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是因为一个助步器老头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is because one Old Man Walker
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顶三个优良壮丁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is worth three good men
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我找不到三个优良壮丁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't find three good men
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.56,0:17:27.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就找了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:27.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I got you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.19,0:17:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的训练现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your training starts now
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但愿能在某个时刻结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And hopefully ends at some point
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先是  消防水管技能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First up, fire hose skills
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:35.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(454,644)}烈火营救
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.63,0:17:51.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:51.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.75,0:17:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.01,0:17:56.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁来救救我的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:56.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone save my baby
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来救你的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll save your baby
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心一点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Careful, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slowly
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.39,0:18:03.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救救我的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:03.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Save my baby
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就听她的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What she said
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.70,0:18:20.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我救下了宝宝  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:20.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saved the baby, chief
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那宝宝的妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what about the mother?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝  宝宝的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The-the mother?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The mother
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.96,0:18:33.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:33.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, men
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功通过训练
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You passed your training
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.63,0:18:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灭了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kill me now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.97,0:18:41.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都是志愿消防员了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:41.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're all volunteer firefighters
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Huzzah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.81,0:18:49.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们消防头盔跟对讲机都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:49.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're out of fire helmets and walkie talkies
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.14,0:18:49.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:49.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, um
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我们上次派对剩的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's some stuff left over from our last party
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.94,0:19:00.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是宠物困在树上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:19:00.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another pet in a tree?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒不如去做更好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got better things to do
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.28,0:19:05.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:05.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look alive, men
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.66,0:19:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的第一项任务来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got your very first assignment
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是点点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Spot
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它困在树上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's stuck in the tree
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.64,0:19:26.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我胡思乱想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:26.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.43,0:19:29.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:29.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.48,0:19:30.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:30.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让它待树上得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He can stay in the tree
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让一让  民众
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step aside, citizen
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.23,0:19:34.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,梯子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:34.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladder
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,急救箱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First aid
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毯子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blanket
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hustle, people
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消防员海绵宝宝呼叫拉里长官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is firefighter SpongeBob to Chief Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救援对象吐了派大星一身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The rescue subject
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just regurgitated all over Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥也被吐到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward got hurled on too
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续加油干
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.56,0:20:07.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:07.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jump
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斑点蜗好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good snail-mation
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.52,0:20:18.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:18.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,附近起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a fire somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真正的火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A real fire
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hustle
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.25,0:20:32.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:32.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消防警报坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The siren is broken
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.00,0:20:34.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能不能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:34.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开船看路  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're going, bozo
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.59,0:20:46.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消防站起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:46.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A fire house on fire
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种讽刺可太劣质了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Talk about your cheap irony
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.72,0:20:50.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:50.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一场火灾出逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The First Fire escaped
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.48,0:21:02.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:02.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Save me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.61,0:21:05.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:05.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.41,0:21:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jump
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是劣质
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that was a rip off
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  大伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, men
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,使出消防水管技能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire hose skills
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍的妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother of Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.01,0:21:28.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  你得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:28.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you're saved
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.18,0:21:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.77,0:21:41.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁需要三个优良壮丁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:41.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did somebody need three good men?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们坚持住  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, hold on in there, you kids
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.26,0:22:12.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早就说过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:12.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell ya
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.43,0:22:14.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,助步器老头顶三个优良壮丁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:14.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old Man Walker is worth three good men?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.52,0:22:16.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:16.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.85,0:22:17.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:17.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.64,0:22:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我救到火了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saved it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我救到了第一场火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saved the First Fire
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.91,0:22:31.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道能不能找点更安全的志愿来做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:31.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can volunteer for something safer
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.28,0:22:33.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,医疗实验
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:33.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Medical experiments
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.91,0:22:34.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着就不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:34.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds good
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.79,0:22:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你今天运气不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your lucky day
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.25,0:22:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是个志愿医生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm also a volunteer doctor
